1
00:00:01,500 --> 00:00:04,596
Once upon a time there was a little girl.

2
00:00:05,396 --> 00:00:08,564
Her name was Goldilocks.

3
00:00:09,364 --> 00:00:12,340
She has blond, curly hair.

4
00:00:13,140 --> 00:00:16,764
One day, she walks in the forest.

5
00:00:17,564 --> 00:00:20,420
She sees a small house.

6
00:00:21,220 --> 00:00:23,836
The door is open.

7
00:00:24,636 --> 00:00:27,876
Goldilocks enters the house.

8
00:00:28,676 --> 00:00:32,684
On the table there are three bowls of soup.

9
00:00:33,484 --> 00:00:36,268
She tries the first soup.

10
00:00:37,068 --> 00:00:40,476
"This soup is too hot!"

11
00:00:41,276 --> 00:00:44,252
She tries the second soup.

12
00:00:45,052 --> 00:00:48,388
"This soup is too cold!"

13
00:00:49,188 --> 00:00:52,044
She tries the third soup.

14
00:00:52,844 --> 00:00:55,964
"This soup is perfect!"

15
00:00:56,764 --> 00:00:59,668
She eats all the soup.

16
00:01:00,468 --> 00:01:03,060
Then she sees three chairs.

17
00:01:03,860 --> 00:01:06,884
She sits on the first chair.

18
00:01:07,684 --> 00:01:10,708
"This chair is too hard!"

19
00:01:11,508 --> 00:01:14,700
She sits on the second chair.

20
00:01:15,500 --> 00:01:18,812
"This chair is too soft!"

21
00:01:19,612 --> 00:01:22,708
She sits on the third chair.

22
00:01:23,508 --> 00:01:26,436
"This chair is perfect!"

23
00:01:27,236 --> 00:01:29,948
But the chair breaks!

24
00:01:30,748 --> 00:01:33,892
Goldilocks falls to the ground.

25
00:01:34,692 --> 00:01:37,788
Then she goes upstairs.

26
00:01:38,588 --> 00:01:41,012
She sees three beds.

27
00:01:41,812 --> 00:01:44,812
She lies on the first bed.

28
00:01:45,612 --> 00:01:48,588
"This bed is too hard!"

29
00:01:49,388 --> 00:01:52,580
She lies on the second bed.

30
00:01:53,380 --> 00:01:56,692
"This bed is too soft!"

31
00:01:57,492 --> 00:02:00,612
She lies on the third bed.

32
00:02:01,412 --> 00:02:04,316
"This bed is perfect!"

33
00:02:05,116 --> 00:02:07,420
She falls asleep.

34
00:02:08,220 --> 00:02:11,436
The three bears come home.

35
00:02:12,236 --> 00:02:17,252
Papa Bear says: "Someone ate my soup!"

36
00:02:18,052 --> 00:02:23,092
Mama Bear says: "Someone ate my soup!"

37
00:02:23,892 --> 00:02:29,316
Little Bear says: "Someone ate all my soup!"

38
00:02:30,116 --> 00:02:35,300
Papa Bear says: "Someone sat on my chair!"

39
00:02:36,100 --> 00:02:40,876
Little Bear says: "Someone broke my chair!"

40
00:02:41,676 --> 00:02:44,724
They go upstairs.

41
00:02:45,524 --> 00:02:50,204
Little Bear says: "Someone is sleeping in my bed!"

42
00:02:51,004 --> 00:02:53,908
Goldilocks wakes up.

43
00:02:54,708 --> 00:02:57,228
She sees the three bears.

44
00:02:58,028 --> 00:03:01,508
"Help!" shouts Goldilocks.

45
00:03:02,308 --> 00:03:05,092
She runs out of the house.

46
00:03:05,892 --> 00:03:08,268
She runs into the forest.

47
00:03:09,068 --> 00:03:11,540
She never comes back.
